{"tid":186883,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 廣東話Kawhi Leonard主題曲 ] 馬刺的可愛（原：浮誇）","createTime":"2017-04-04T13:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T10:06:38.000Z","uid":47374,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e47a49e410b99c4d75a6c44743974df45d8d916d","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHH15cm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHH15cm.jpg&h=8958aebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1832207810365522/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Frealcoach%2Fvideos%2F1832207810365522%2F&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ba51e4d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1832207810365522/</a><br />\n<br />\n無辨法唔歌頌Kawhi呢個馬刺嘅巨星<br />\n可愛嘅性格、強效嘅防守、星味濃嘅進攻<br />\n加上Mark Tai 激唱嘅浮誇，請多多Share！<br />\n<br />\n記得tag朋友聽，我IG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/realbasketballcoach/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Frealbasketballcoach%2F&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=379f87f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/realbasketballcoach/</a><br />\n-----------------<br />\n原：浮誇 (陳奕迅)<br />\n詞：正宗教練<br />\n唱：戴晉揚 Mark Tai<br />\n<br />\n以前仲細 教練發火 日日哦哦哦<br />\n我磨練夠其實會著晒火 今晚爆邊個<br />\n我臂展長 成日想去 搶你個波<br />\n偷到我又有樽鋤<br />\n球快攻 未離地 就已經 比我格咗<br />\n遇到我等於折磨<br />\n<br />\n仲練埋射三分　練嚟為咗更易打爆敵人<br />\n木獨過一生 學鄧肯寶訓<br />\n贏完唔笑嘅我至係最狠<br />\n<br />\n馬刺我大權當道 波波都知我恐怖<br />\n有敵人要突圍中路 守鬼到佢燥<br />\n時代替換唔怕　我繼續嚟開路<br />\n出啲高比嘅招數<br />\n我盡情喪射 唔用套<br />\n今晚夠數 波波無力嘈<br />\n任我轟多十零廿鋪<br />\n<br />\n第二年入playoff 罰球射失<br />\n我仲hurt過達哥<br />\n練習更加多　令熱火知錯<br />\n場場完爆你 叫我做契哥<br />\n<br />\n馬刺我大權當道 啲街坊都知我恐怖<br />\n有敵人要突圍中路 守鬼到佢燥<br />\n我決心打到老 靠我未來開路<br />\n出啲高比嘅招數<br />\n我盡情喪射 唔用套<br />\n今晚夠數 波波無力嘈<br />\n任我癲返十零廿鋪<br />\n<br />\n成隊勇士夠膽砌多鋪<br />\n快睇我Solo 我苦練完實進步<br />\n盡全力殺埋入下個Final"},{"pid":"8fb209622b73f4e231bd41c88cc4aabc6cf885fc","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b9afb3c0c166575aea8c9155491017dda887520b","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:01:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ad99fb4d1bffab516cf3c3ff4ad9c80dcc0e2a79","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d773b3efe2fd8009b1bed0e3b58295331c40cf6f","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3fbdcee8d28ecd92e4c1c6947512d99632548e7c","tid":186883,"uid":30719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:39:36.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd03324fd215e51358a9ef9fbd22783e21e2505","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝！"},{"pid":"12b322987b5218e358159112f05b9f36c2b58153","tid":186883,"uid":13930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"下首作邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eb3a5a2d02851f9b01236fbf9110b7107e18da","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下首作邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係西書 kobe dirk"},{"pid":"ccdd4e6d2b4d2afab0ddbe856e3b008606698656","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8d6e0fe8239f251a98309f3caf665cf6a0e9287c","tid":186883,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike